cassandra-reaper (0.2.3-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Add config option for default ScheduleDaysBetween
  * REST API: Get repair schedule by keyspace[+cluster], get clusters by seed
  * Decrease scheduler wakeup time to 10 minutes
  * Cancel all running repairs on nodes where Reaper has no commands running

